<lb n="0356a17"/>咖<note place="inline">去</note>&CB01222;伽訶那<note place="inline">十</note><anchor id="fxT19p0356a01"/>薩婆何<anchor id="fxT19p0356a02"/>婆婆舜<note place="inline">入</note>提<note place="inline">十一</note>阿
<lb n="0356a18"/>鼻詵者麼蘇伽陀跋囉跋繕那<note place="inline">十二</note>阿蜜&CB00069;多
